export const homeObjectone = {
  primary: true,
  lightBg: true,
  lightTopLine: false,
  lightText: false,
  lightTextDesc: false,
  topLine: 'Dhyana Sloka',
  headline: 'Your Favourite Devotional YouTube Channel',
  description:
    'Put always God first. He is the one who can help you everytime. The only way you can get bhagavat Krupa is constant chanting of slokas.Dhyana sloka channel presents  slokas which you can recite, listen every day.We wish you recite these slokas and follow bhakti maarga.',
  buttonLabel: 'Get Started',
  imgStart: '',
  img: require('../../images/svspp.png'),
  alt: 'About',
  start: ''
};

export const homeObjectTwo = {
  primary: true,
  lightBg: false,
  lightTopLine: true,
  lightText: true,
  lightTextDesc: true,
  topLine: 'Playlists based on Month',
  headline: 'Listen to Dhyana slokas based on Maasam (Month) speciality.',
  description:
    "Constant Listening and Chanting to the slokas will give inner peace. Please note that we publish only stotram or slokam in our channel. Mantra upadesha should be given by guru alone and not via public media",
  buttonLabel: 'Learn More',
  imgStart: '',
  img: require('../../images/maasam.png'),
  alt: 'Playlist',
  start: ''
};

export const homeObjectThree = {
  primary: false,
  lightBg: true,
  lightTopLine: false,
  lightText: false,
  lightTextDesc: false,
  topLine: 'Subscribe Dhyana Sloka Channel',
  headline:
    'Receive most powerful slokas and Chant them every day',
  description:
    "We will upload one video every week based on the Maasam/ Upcoming Festivals and your Request in the comments section in YouTube",
  buttonLabel: 'Please visit our channel',
  imgStart: 'start',
  img: require('../../images/logo.png'),
  alt: 'Subscription',
  start: 'true'
};
